short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A simple client-side extension that converts DocSend documents to PDFs securely and efficiently.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
All converting is done locally (not online), all you have to do is open up DocSend and press the convert button. No more sharing sensitive documents, passwords, or emails insecurely.

Choose between high-res and low-res rendering to optimize image quality or storage space.

Free trial and money back guarantee. Email for support anytime.
